Com aviDemoWidth (cvar)
=======================

Description
-----------

Select the width of the .[TGA](TGA\_(file\_format)) frames generated with the [aviDemo](AviDemo\_(console\_command)) command.

Usage
-----

At the console type...

`com_aviDemoWidth [int]`

Parameters
----------

-   [int] - A positive value for the amount of horizontal pixels.

